scoringPlays.text: David Bailey 1 Yd Run (Danny Longman Kick)
Mataeo Durant 49 Yd Run (Charlie Ham PAT failed)
Hunter Long 9 Yd pass from Phil Jurkovec (Danny Longman PAT failed)
Zay Flowers 61 Yd pass from Phil Jurkovec (Danny Longman Kick)

videos.headline: Bailey's TD gets Boston College on the board first
videos.description: Boston College RB David Bailey takes the handoff and forces his way across the goal line for a touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Bailey’s TD gets Boston College on the board first) 2020/09/19 ESHEET

videos.headline: Duke's Gilbert makes leaping INT
videos.description: Boston College QB Phil Jurkovec throws the ball downfield, but Duke DB Mark Gilbert jumps up to make the interception.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Duke’s Gilbert makes leaping INT) 2020/09/19 ESHEET

videos.headline: Durant breaks free for long Duke TD
videos.description: Duke RB Mataeo Durant takes the handoff and rushes 49 yards into the end zone for the score.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Durant breaks free for long Duke TD) 2020/09/19 ESHEET

videos.headline: BC's McDuffie in the right place at the right time for INT
videos.description: Duke QB Chase Brice tries to throw across the middle, but Boston College LB Isaiah McDuffie is in the right place for the interception.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (BC’s McDuffie in the right place at the right time for INT) 2020/09/19 ESHEET

videos.headline: BC's DeBerry strips ball while falling to the ground
videos.description: Duke WR Damond Philyaw-Johnson makes the catch, but Boston College DB Josh DeBerry strips the ball away and recovers it while attempting a tackle.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (BC’s DeBerry strips ball while falling to the ground) 2020/09/19 ESHEET

videos.headline: BC's Long makes one-handed grab while being held
videos.description: Boston College TE Hunter Long secures a catch with one hand while his other arm is being held by a defender.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (BC’s Long makes one-handed grab while being held) 2020/09/19 ESHEET

videos.headline: BC's Brice avoids sack for TD pass
videos.description: Boston College QB Chase Brice avoids getting sacked and then finds TE Hunter Long in the back of the end zone for a touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (BC’s Brice avoids sack for TD pass) 2020/09/19 ESHEET

videos.headline: BC's Flowers left all alone for 61-yard TD catch
videos.description: Boston College QB Chase Brice connects with a wide-open WR Zay Flowers for a 61-yard touchdown play.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (BC’s Flowers left all alone for 61-yard TD catch) 2020/09/19 ESHEET
